document_data.name: Wharf Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Wharf Street''' was a small road that was located in the city of [[Waterdeep]].{{Cite interactive atlas|Waterdeep}}
document_data.Location: Wharf Street was located in the south section of Waterdeep's [[Waterdeep/Dock Ward|Dock Ward]]. It branched south off of [[Spices Street]] then turned southwest to terminate on [[Dock Street (Waterdeep)|Dock Street]] on the waterfront.
